culture at its best this is an amazing book , practically one of a kind ! the information , illustions , and luster of the indigenous african cultures is beautiful to behold . i recommed introducing young children to cultures and peoples as varied as the come to fully portray to them the true beauty of this creation , life . there is nothing so intricate , so inveloping and powerful as life in this form . pronounciation is given for the tribes names to bring ease of reading , which is , in fact , very enjoyable